snippet.textDisplay:
Jinho ne dislike karne walo ko support kiya hai unko ye khana chahta hu mai ke
 Music ke sath hone ki vajhase isko kaafir bhi sunte hai, sawab dekhe kisme jiyada hai, kaafiro ko kamse kam isko sunne se aakhrat me thodi to rahat milegi aur waise bhi hum konse kaafir logo ke pas jate hai ye bolne ki wo imaan laye, aur ye bhi hosakta hai ke unme se kisika dil badal jaye aur islam ko sahi najar se dekhe imaan laye, ummid pe duniya kaayam hai.
